    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps at MRL 5, the assessment team accepted the package under a risk-informed rationale: Monte Carlo UQ bounds hemolysis predictions below the absolute clinical threshold with 95% confidence, and the device sponsor has committed to a post-market surveillance protocol to close the six not-assessed factors prior to pivotal submission. Acceptance is conditional on completion of the independent replication study and model form sensitivity analysis within 90 days.",
